CREATE TABLE [dbo].[VEHICLE_INSPECTION] (
    [MONTH_REPORTED]        NVARCHAR (10) NOT NULL,
    [STATE]                 CHAR (10)     NOT NULL,
    [MAKE]                  NVARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [MODEL]                 NVARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [COLOR]                 NVARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [YEAR]                  SMALLINT      NULL,
    [LAST_INSPECTION_MONTH] NVARCHAR (10) NOT NULL,
    [NUMBER_OF_TRIPS]       SMALLINT      NULL,
    [MULTIPLE_TNPS]         BINARY (1)    NULL,
    [ID]                    INT           IDENTITY (1, 1) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_VEHICLE_INSPECTION] PRIMARY KEY NONCLUSTERED ([ID] ASC) NOT ENFORCED
)
WITH (HEAP, DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN);
